cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.AI. 

This paper deals with view updates in relational database management systems, which is a core topic in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The use of Datalog to describe update strategies involves logic programming (cs.PL) and the validation algorithm proposed in the paper involves formal methods (cs.LO). The optimization algorithm for user-written programs involves software engineering (cs.SE) and the use of Datalog for view updates has applications in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for knowledge representation and reasoning.
